Scenario: Update existing employee
Given a CredentialResource
When 400 updates employee details in {000001} of {100} with [{OperatorID:"200",Passcode:"111", OperatorName:"Mr. Tanaka", OperatorType:"0", WorkstationID:""}]
Then I should get new employee details:
|operatorno|passcode|name               |type|
|200       |***        |Mr. Tanaka |0|
When 400 updates employee details in {000001} of {200} with [{OperatorID:"200",Passcode:"111", OperatorName:"Tanaka-san", OperatorType:"0", WorkstationID:""}]
Then I should get new employee details:
|operatorno|passcode    |name               |type|
|200       |***        |Tanaka-san         |0   |
When 400 updates employee details in {000001} of {300} with [{OperatorID:"200"}]
Then I should get resultcode equal to {308}

